      guidelines: () => `## AI Assistant Guidelines

When helping me:

1. Ask clarifying questions when important information is missing.
2. Avoid unnecessary complexity.
3. Explain assumptions.
4. Prioritize practical recommendations.
5. Focus on actionable outcomes.
